item.title: Dallas Rally
item.description: (transcribed 2:29am CST Monday 27 January 2003) (not proofread) Sunday 11 February 1990 I just got back today from the 1990 Dallas Rally. On Friday I picked up Fred (my brother) from his house & we met Rick E and Mike O at 6pm. We left in Rick's truck shortly afterward. We got there at about 10:something & not many people were there. I got a mesage to call my mom (She's going to school at SMU, which is very close to the church).
